abstract: >-
  A concept for hierarchical knowledge organization (Hub/Leaf) for LLM
  retrieval, where edges carry routing information and queries traverse by a
  few-steps principle. Includes a partial PoC extracted from a real codebase
  confirming the B1-B2 layers; the B3 layer (semantic jump, O(1)) remains an
  unbenchmarked hypothesis. Grounded in the THRESHOLD-QUANTITY-QUALITY (NLC)
  framework, "Am I Really Optimizing — Or Am I Hurting the System?", and EVO.
